1> Setting up buissness network

Start the creation process for business network using Yeoman Generator. Run this command on a terminal.

yo hyperledger-composer:businessnetwork

Provide the network name as supplychain-network and add the information for description, author name, and author email.
This will also ask for license, provide Apache-2.0 as the license. This is an open-source license.
After that  add the namespace . Here we are using org.supplychain.network as the namespace.
Finally, select No when asked whether to generate an empty network or not.
After this , skeleton network will be generated

